Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:48.05,Main,Enta,0,0,0,,我  得救了嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:48.89,Main,Kazuki,0,0,0,,悠…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.03,Main,Toi,0,0,0,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:54.20,Main,Toi,0,0,0,,我如果是你  也會選擇救陣內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:58.21,Main,Toi,0,0,0,,但是我已經累了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.71,Main,Kazuki,0,0,0,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.13,Main,Otter,0,0,0,,胡說！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:08.97,Main,Otter,0,0,0,,來吧  把這個世界上的聯繫全部切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.47,Main,,0,0,120,,絕望 : 解放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:22.03,Main,Keppi,0,0,0,,Dadadadadadadadadadada...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:24.31,Main,Keppi,0,0,0,,Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.04,Main,Kazuki,0,0,0,,悠！
